==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mac
<hw>Mac</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>Shortened form of
<altname>Macintosh</altname>, a brand name for a personal computer;
<as>as, the latest <ex>Mac</ex> has great new features</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

