<hw>Mac</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Gael., son.]</ety> <def>A prefix, in
names of Scotch origin, signifying <sig>son</sig>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

