==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: mac
<hw>mac</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Shortened form of
<altname>mackintosh</altname>, a waterproof raincoat made of rubberized
fabric.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mackintosh, mac, mack.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

